WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.481
Well, good evening family. Thank you for joining us again tonight, and good morning to all of you in Australia.

00:00:06.482 --> 00:00:13.716
I don't know what time it is over there, but I like to say good morning all the time, even when it is not morning.

00:00:13.717 --> 00:00:24.355
We have a lot to talk about tonight. We have these clips Braden made for us, and he'll be adding new things to the back of the screen.

00:00:24.356 --> 00:00:37.631
He works so hard at it. I told him, 'Let's do two nights in a row of that.'He worked so hard on the prophetic mural.

00:00:37.632 --> 00:00:43.197
It's needed, even though my head's covering all of it. Well, you weren't here last night, that's why.

00:00:43.198 --> 00:00:55.199
But I'd rather have you here than that. Come get closer to me. Let's go over some of the things in the news.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:01:15.630
I want to start right off by saying this: I thought it was amazing last night because I went over everything the Lord showed us at the end of the broadcast—when it happened, how it happened, and everything.

00:01:15.631 --> 00:01:27.079
Excuse me, that's why I'm sitting. I just had greasy food. I took a bite of that bread.

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:37.910
It wasn't until I said, 'Don't you see? I can't do anything. I don't have control of it,'and it was a flatline.

00:01:37.911 --> 00:01:54.719
It was like touching a cold stove last night. But the moment I gave Jesus the praise, the moment I acknowledged him, it switched on and I started seeing.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:02:08.579
He said, 'If you give me praise and glory and touch not the glory, touch not the anointing, every time you do this, I'll show up like that.'But last night I didn't, because I don't want to be redundant.

00:02:08.580 --> 00:02:14.719
It's like repeating things over and over again. Brandon can't do anything apart from him.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:21.300
Anything I see, anything that's shown to us by the spirit of God, is all because of God.

00:02:21.301 --> 00:02:26.959
I say it every single time and I'll continue to say it. Last night was a perfect example.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:30.879
I avoided trying to go over it, and there it was—it was a flatline.

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:56.639
I did the whole broadcast and showed you all the things until I said, 'Well, excuse me, here we are folks.'I thought it was amazing because the moment I gave him acknowledgement, the moment I said it out of my mouth—apart from him, I can do nothing; we give all the glory to Jesus—I started seeing instantaneously.

00:02:56.640 --> 00:03:07.883
It was amazing. The broadcast went on for three hours. I said I couldn't get in the river no matter how hard I tried.

00:03:07.884 --> 00:03:15.115
Even today, whenever he took me and I was in my prayer time, he said, 'Brandon'—I said, 'What is going on?

00:03:15.116 --> 00:03:17.658
How are things going today?'just talking like I always do to him.

00:03:17.659 --> 00:03:25.639
And he said, 'Brandon, I want you to start enjoying life more. You're taking too much of this on you.

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:38.159
I want you to have fun and enjoy life.'I said, 'I get it.'He said, 'Tell my people to have more fun.

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:44.959
Tell my people to enjoy life more. Life's supposed to be fun and good.

00:03:44.960 --> 00:04:01.433
I gave you life, and life more abundantly.'So many people are like me—the pressure of life, the pressure of the prophetic, the pressure of all of it tries to choke the fun out of things.

00:04:01.434 --> 00:04:08.799
He said, 'I want you just to have fun. Laugh more. Enjoy your family more.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:19.559
You don't have to walk under the pressure of things. It's not yours to carry.'Yesterday was a prime example of it.

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:26.643
I remember Rodney Howard-Browne telling a story—and I don't talk about names, but I remember this story.

00:04:26.644 --> 00:04:37.753
He brought it up to me where he was over at some pastor's house before the service and he was playing video games with the pastor's son.

00:04:37.754 --> 00:04:47.919
The pastor got so upset that he was not praying before the service; he was not taking it more seriously in his mind.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:05:00.898
But Rodney felt to play the game with the son, and the glory fell in that service. The bottom line is, it is in us.

00:05:00.899 --> 00:05:10.444
Regardless of whether you're having fun and enjoying life, or you're relaxing and resting, there's a point where you think it's self-righteousness that brings the glory.

00:05:10.445 --> 00:05:38.439
'Well, it's because I fasted five times this week,'and 'It's because I put myself in position.'Not saying that doesn't help your flesh to be crucified, but if you have the mindset that it's because of what I did that got me qualified to get this, you already disqualified yourself. The Lord was showing me it's about relationship.

00:05:38.440 --> 00:06:04.964
He said, 'Brandon, it's about relationship.'Do you realize it's not about how much you think—'I didn't say anything rude today to Diana; I tried really hard to always walk in love'—when you're in a marriage and you work with somebody seven days a week, 24 hours a day, you have a tendency to be cranky and crunchy.

00:06:04.965 --> 00:06:13.100
I tell her, 'It's not about even that.''Well, I disqualified myself today; I had a bad attitude.'You always want to walk in love, but that's not the point.

00:06:13.101 --> 00:06:28.319
I'm trying to say that it's not how good you think you are that qualifies you for the glory.

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:39.439
You're human, and you always lean on him. You are always leaning on and trusting in him regardless of how messed up you are.

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:49.039
It's all about Jesus. It's just a mindset of relationship that he's been teaching me about.

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:59.652
It's always something like, 'Well, I prayed extra long today.'We drove a lot more today and looked for stuff for our eBay store.

00:06:59.653 --> 00:07:08.559
'You prayed a lot longer today, Brandon. Boy, I bet tonight's broadcast is going to be over the top because you prayed in tongues for six hours.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:17.279
I bet you're qualified tonight, buddy.'That's why the Lord told me, 'Brandon, even on your worst day, it's my grace.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:27.127
No matter how much you have it in your mind to think that you're qualified tonight to see and be able to do anything in the spirit realm with me, you never were good enough in the first place.

00:07:27.128 --> 00:07:34.469
It was always by my grace and by the blood.'It goes back to when I stepped on the dog and killed it.

00:07:34.470 --> 00:07:42.879
If anyone hasn't heard that before, my little girl got a dog for Christmas.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:49.425
Diana, I'm glad you're here; you can chime in. Don't sit over there and be quiet.

00:07:49.426 --> 00:07:58.594
I was playing Warzone, Call of Duty, with Braden for Christmas.

00:07:58.595 --> 00:08:05.319
I'm really competitive and we like to win. Braden's really good at Call of Duty.

00:08:05.320 --> 00:08:07.970
For all the religious ones out there: Oh my gosh, I can't believe...

00:08:07.971 --> 00:08:23.037
No, no, no. I have fun with my son and we play as a team. Braden wins; he's very good at Call of Duty. I'm not so good.

00:08:23.038 --> 00:08:28.352
I was really focused and wasn't paying attention, but I told Paisley to put the dog up several times.

00:08:28.353 --> 00:08:42.894
It was a brand new puppy and she had it wrapped in a blanket. I jumped up to go to the bathroom in between matches.

00:08:42.895 --> 00:08:50.354
I'm a big guy, of course, and I stepped on this puppy and killed it right there.

00:08:50.355 --> 00:09:00.634
Squashed it. The guts popped out. I mean, this is how I squashed and destroyed this dog right there.

00:09:00.635 --> 00:09:08.175
Instantaneously, Paisley is like, 'You—'because the dog is dead. I lost it.

00:09:08.176 --> 00:09:13.442
I'm cussing, acting a fool, because I'm so mad about what I just did.

00:09:13.443 --> 00:09:17.424
I'm blaming myself, but instantaneously you start blaming other people.

00:09:17.425 --> 00:09:23.679
'It's your fault.'No, it's my fault. I was stupid. I should have watched where I was walking.

00:09:23.680 --> 00:09:28.639
But I lost my cool and started saying all kinds of profanity.

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:37.639
I was freaking out because the dog we just bought for Christmas was dead; it had been squashed.

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:49.199
This was years ago. I just want to clarify that this was a long time ago.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:10:01.449
You don't have to defend me; it is what it is. I was a jerk and killed the dog. I lost it.

00:10:01.450 --> 00:10:11.199
I went in the back and Paisley started screaming, 'Daddy, aren't you going to pray for my dog to rise from the dead?

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:20.086
Daddy, don't you believe God will raise my dog from the dead?'I said, 'God's not going to hear me at all. Honey, I'm not there. I lost it.

00:10:20.087 --> 00:10:31.839
I'm just not there.'I said, 'But you pray; I can't.'She said, 'All things are possible to him who believes, Daddy.

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:39.399
Pray for my dog to get up from the dead.'I told her I couldn't do it and that He wouldn't hear me.

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:50.110
So she started marching up and down the hallway, screaming as loud as she could, 'All things are possible!'praying in the Holy Spirit, 'Get up from the dead, dog!

00:10:50.111 --> 00:10:59.899
Get up from the dead!'She was weeping because her dog was dead. Several hours later, Diana put the dog in a shoebox.

00:10:59.900 --> 00:11:15.460
It was frozen outside with snow on the ground, and I thought, 'I'm not going to go out there and dig a hole in that frozen ground right now.'So we put the dog in a shoebox and set it by the trash can on the front porch.

00:11:15.461 --> 00:11:31.203
I told her I'd take care of it later. Diana put the dog out there and I felt bad later.

00:11:31.204 --> 00:11:37.399
The Holy Spirit jumped all over me because I had acted like an idiot.

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:42.438
I was broken. I went in and told her I was sorry. Paisley was still crying.

00:11:42.439 --> 00:12:02.730
I admitted I was an idiot and apologized for yelling. Then Diana went to take the trash out to the porch, and the dog was gone. She came in and said, 'Brandon, the dog is gone.

00:12:02.731 --> 00:12:19.664
Something got it.'I thought because we lived in the country, raccoons or a stray cat had taken the puppy to eat because it was cold.

00:12:19.665 --> 00:12:35.644
Then she heard a squeaking noise. Diana went down and looked, and that dog was alive.

00:12:35.645 --> 00:12:41.326
It was frozen cold, but all the guts and blood were gone. It was completely restored—no guts, no blood, nothing.

00:12:41.327 --> 00:12:57.519
That dog had been completely mushed; I had crushed the bones, but it was completely restored by the power of God.

00:12:57.520 --> 00:13:01.807
Diana brought the dog in, started blow-drying it, and got it warm.

00:13:01.808 --> 00:13:32.062
Paisley sat there with the biggest grin on her face and said, 'Daddy, I told you all things are possible to him who believes.'To this day, I'll never forget her little face, nor your face, nor Braden's face.

00:13:32.063 --> 00:13:41.156
We were all in awe of the goodness of God and the shock of what had happened.

00:13:41.157 --> 00:13:54.319
I held that dog in my hand, and God spoke to me. He said, 'Even on your best day, son, your righteousness is filthy rags.

00:13:54.320 --> 00:14:12.719
In the natural, without my Son's blood, you're never good enough.'God brought that back to me today regarding the mantle we walk in.

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:29.719
No matter how you live your life, it's about keeping a relationship with Him and keeping the main thing the main thing, but not touching the trigger. What's God's trigger? Touching the glory.

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:49.152
Apart from Him, Jesus said, 'I only do what my Father tells me to do.'He did not separate Himself from His Father's voice but always deflected and gave God the praise.

00:14:49.153 --> 00:14:56.478
If the Son of God always gave God the praise, we must do the same.

00:14:56.479 --> 00:15:04.606
In everything you do in word and deed, give all to the glory of God.

00:15:04.607 --> 00:15:12.489
The Bible says that in all we do and say, in word and deed, give all to the glory of God.

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:24.276
No matter what you're going through, we give all to the glory of God; we stay on God's side.

00:15:24.277 --> 00:15:42.639
As I walked through that, the Lord reminded me—because it was around the same time of year, January—to look back at the Rolodex of miracles seen in life.

00:15:42.640 --> 00:15:48.559
You realize that even then, your righteousness is filthy rags.

00:15:48.560 --> 00:16:13.838
The point the Lord was trying to tell me was, 'Brandon, when you give me praise, it opens the door for the blessing.'When you acknowledge Him and tell people, no matter the size of your platform, that you can't do anything apart from Him, it matters.

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:22.228
Seeing things coming in the future is a gift from Him to show us what is coming.

00:16:22.229 --> 00:16:28.246
Joel chapter 2 says that young men will see visions and old men will dream dreams.

00:16:28.247 --> 00:16:38.479
People ridicule this, but God said, 'Brandon, I'm just fulfilling what I told you I'd do in my Word.

00:16:38.480 --> 00:17:05.639
Someone has to fit the role; why not you?'My young men will have visions, my old men will dream dreams, and I'll pour out my Spirit upon my handmaidens.

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:16.319
Whether it's Acts chapter 2 or Joel chapter 2, God is fulfilling what He said He would do in the last days.

00:17:16.320 --> 00:17:44.199
How many visions qualify? 'Visions'is plural; it doesn't mean singular. He's saying multiple. Old men will have multiple dreams.

00:17:44.200 --> 00:18:01.719
If you push into Him and give Him glory, He will show you much more to come, and it will prove accurate. It will be a sign for the world to know He is coming.

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:16.919
The main mission for this channel is to tell His people He is coming and that it's time to repent and get serious about the Father coming.

00:18:16.920 --> 00:18:31.570
I said I'd do it. We set out to raise a prayer channel with a million prayer warriors on YouTube.

00:18:31.571 --> 00:18:44.279
By doing so, you will change the course of things. Stand strong, keep in His Word, and always deflect the glory.

00:18:44.280 --> 00:19:22.975
It's not about Brandon or Diana. I will not take His glory. Last night in the spirit, we saw Trump negotiating major deals with the Greenland people.

00:19:22.976 --> 00:19:33.719
Europe and the EU were standing strong against Trump, saying they wouldn't allow it. I saw them divided in half.

00:19:33.720 --> 00:19:47.279
The elders in Greenland did not want to join the United States, but the young people did.

00:19:47.280 --> 00:20:04.358
They were going to take a major vote to become part of the United States. The Trump administration was after minerals.

00:20:04.359 --> 00:20:16.296
I saw billions of dollars of minerals to build batteries and things like that. What else was in the dirt?

00:20:16.297 --> 00:20:23.439
I saw big dump trucks circling around; they were going down and getting the minerals.

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:37.848
I saw fish, which I thought related to cobalt. You're still going, right?

00:20:37.849 --> 00:20:45.163
No, I want you to tell me. We'll bring our American stores to your shores.

00:20:45.164 --> 00:20:56.436
I saw American stores and big companies going to Greenland to make it like America, like we would do anywhere else.

00:20:56.437 --> 00:21:11.479
You're part of us now, so we'll share what we have. An IHOP is going to come there, or a Denny's where you can eat breakfast at night.

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:23.528
McDonald's is probably already there. Starbucks is just around the corner on every block.

00:21:23.529 --> 00:21:27.319
I cracked myself up; it's not even funny, but it's funny to me.

00:21:27.320 --> 00:21:37.159
Dunkin'Donuts is going right next door. I saw all these major things coming.

00:21:37.160 --> 00:21:46.253
This is what we saw last night. Less than 24 hours, folks, and it happens in the news.

00:21:46.254 --> 00:21:57.443
A lot of times, when we would see things in the past before we started getting on the channel, some things would take two to three months or two to three years.

00:21:57.444 --> 00:22:16.554
He warned us about COVID before we were even on YouTube. He told us that summer that a major shaking was coming, and it started happening by March of 2019, I think.

00:22:16.555 --> 00:22:28.437
He spoke to us in 2018. He told us COVID was coming, and then he told us another virus is coming after that.

00:22:28.438 --> 00:22:46.249
Read that one right there: 'Trump admin reportedly considers paying each Greenland resident up to 100k amid US takeover talks'—that came out today.

00:22:46.250 --> 00:23:17.199
How much did I tell you they would offer them? I saw that the real agreement, whenever it really came down to it, was over $25,000 per citizen to buy their country with our US tax dollars.

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:27.263
I saw these major things taking place last night in prayer, and it's in the news today, less than 12 hours later.

00:23:27.264 --> 00:23:31.136
People ask, 'Do you work at the news agency, Brandon? How did you know that?

00:23:31.137 --> 00:23:35.885
Do you work for the CIA?'I've heard that so much lately. 'You must be Mossad.

00:23:35.886 --> 00:23:40.640
You work for Mossad. CIA, you're an operative. I know you are.

00:23:40.641 --> 00:23:50.704
You're part of the Masonics, part of that 666 stuff with the witchcraft.'Come on, folks.

00:23:50.705 --> 00:23:54.895
I'm a Holy Ghost believer, baptized in the Holy Ghost, praying in the Holy Ghost.

00:23:54.896 --> 00:24:07.855
I'm not CIA. I don't work for Mossad. It's Jesus. Isn't he wonderful? That's all I can say to your ignorance.

00:24:07.856 --> 00:24:22.340
Read this one right here: 'US considering investing in critical minerals mining in Greenland, Ammaroq CEO tells CNBC.'That happened today.

00:24:22.341 --> 00:24:29.283
What did Brandon say? What did the Holy Ghost say they were after?

00:24:29.284 --> 00:24:42.508
I saw major mining, and it was going to establish the dollar against the BRICS. All this is to combat the BRICS. The dollar is in trouble.

00:24:42.509 --> 00:24:48.059
As you see behind us on the screen, the dollar is in trouble and it's about to go over the waterfall.

00:24:48.060 --> 00:24:54.608
Trump is paddling as fast as he can; he's canoeing and fighting to keep our economy up.

00:24:54.609 --> 00:25:03.479
The Lord said, 'Pray for him,'for I heard impeachment will come again in 2026 or 2027.

00:25:03.480 --> 00:25:15.554
They'll say it a lot, but they'll not have the votes because we'll keep the House.

00:25:15.555 --> 00:25:32.881
The Lord said the Senate is in jeopardy. You have a great opportunity to lose the Senate.

00:25:32.882 --> 00:25:40.029
I saw them losing the Senate in November, and the Lord said you must pray to keep it.

00:25:40.030 --> 00:25:49.858
There are key races in key places where intercessory prayer will have great influence.

00:25:49.859 --> 00:25:59.898
We're going to continue to pray that we get the Senate and the House so that Trump doesn't have a stalemate presidency.

00:25:59.899 --> 00:26:15.512
Behind us, I saw Elon Musk coming back on the scene. The bromance is back.

00:26:15.513 --> 00:26:24.013
Elon's back. Trump's back. I knew he was coming back. I told everybody how many times?

00:26:24.014 --> 00:26:37.662
I got detailed about what I saw concerning that man with the rockets.

00:26:37.663 --> 00:26:51.496
Where did SpaceX come from? Who does he have a covenant with?

00:26:51.497 --> 00:27:21.039
The Lord said, 'Who did he have a relationship with for his first rocket?'If you look at the trail at the beginning, you'll find it was cheaper to go to another country.

00:27:21.040 --> 00:27:27.999
That country gave him the ability to do what he's doing right now, which translated to America.

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:46.802
But it all started somewhere. What lies beneath the surface?

00:27:46.803 --> 00:28:06.985
The Lord warned us to pray about these things. He keeps warning us about Cuba.

00:28:06.986 --> 00:28:15.813
This is a prayer fail that happened last night. Play the video.

00:28:15.814 --> 00:28:25.650
Regarding the church in Salt Lake City, they say you're derogatory, but I'm trying to tell you that you're going to be targeted.

00:28:25.651 --> 00:28:34.119
You need to pray over the main Mormon base in Utah. I saw mass casualties coming.

00:28:34.120 --> 00:28:53.544
I see Salt Lake City; it's the area for the Mormons. I see an attack concerning certain landmarks represented in 2026.

00:28:53.545 --> 00:29:04.809
There's something about Utah that is highlighted. It goes clear up into Seattle; I'm talking mass events.

00:29:04.810 --> 00:29:19.755
A deadly mass shooting in Salt Lake City and the hunt for whoever pulled the trigger—two people killed, eight shot, three in critical condition at a funeral at an LDS church along Redwood Road.

00:29:19.756 --> 00:29:45.387
I said the Mormon church in Salt Lake City. The more I flow in this, the greater detail in the vision, the greater the threat.

00:29:45.388 --> 00:30:06.993
If it's bold and very clear, it's very prominent. This is a very serious situation at hand.

00:30:06.994 --> 00:30:24.040
When it's faded and not as detailed or vibrant, it's not coming as quick. It's not a heightened alert that I want.

00:30:24.041 --> 00:30:26.079
I don't want to say it's not coming as quick; it's just not heightened as much.

00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:32.283
This is serious. You need to really pray. The more vibrant the colors, the more things I see.

00:30:32.284 --> 00:30:40.999
This is something that's very hot. Did I describe that well enough? You understand what I'm saying?

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:48.350
Well, you're married to me, but you get it because I'm trying, and you know what I'm saying all the time.

00:30:48.351 --> 00:30:56.769
The greater the vision, the greater the detail, the greater the prayer.

00:30:56.770 --> 00:31:00.759
More imminent. More imminent. There you go. Thank you for the word.

00:31:00.760 --> 00:31:04.799
So I try to tell everybody it's very close. And then how many days later?

00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:10.959
November 13th, I see this. Today's the 7th of January and it happened.

00:31:10.960 --> 00:31:20.320
And the Lord says there's more to come. Now I don't know how—is it open doors or whatever?

00:31:20.321 --> 00:31:26.757
But the Lord says, 'Pray for the Mormon church in this time frame.'Do I follow their false doctrine?

00:31:26.758 --> 00:31:38.839
Yes. I'm not here to attack any religion or denomination, but I have to tell you the truth. What I know is false doctrine.

00:31:38.840 --> 00:31:43.945
And the Lord said, 'I'm bringing a great revival to the Mormon church, and I'm going to shake the Mormon church.

00:31:43.946 --> 00:31:50.826
In doing so, I'm going to show up, and there's going to be a splitting of the Mormon church.

00:31:50.827 --> 00:32:19.502
You're going to see a major split but a major revival happen in the midst of it, for there are really good people there.'That's why I said I'm not trying to be derogatory; that was what that was about because I said it's false, but the Lord said, 'I'm going to shake the Mormon church and there's going to be a major revival there.'So Braden makes those shorts and I try to tell you what is happening.

00:32:19.503 --> 00:32:28.359
What I was saying about it before, number two, what I see in Seattle: another major attack's coming.

00:32:28.360 --> 00:32:35.596
I saw it all over the place. The Lord showed me. And so we saw a major earthquake taking place there.

00:32:35.597 --> 00:32:45.973
We saw Yellowstone going off. We've seen major earthquakes in Yellowstone National Park.

00:32:45.974 --> 00:32:49.812
In British Columbia, we saw volcanoes going off in the water.

00:32:49.812 --> 00:33:03.769
We saw major tsunami waves coming in when we've seen Cuba plotting a plan to attack us with some kind of biological thing in the days ahead and make it look like it's drug traffickers.

00:33:03.770 --> 00:33:10.559
They'll use drug traffickers as the cover of this. It's not drug traffickers; it's Cuba.

00:33:10.560 --> 00:33:18.639
It's the government. Watch what happens. This is one that's encouraging.

00:33:18.640 --> 00:33:24.934
Now, I try to give you both sides of the coin all the time, what the Holy Ghost is talking to us about.

00:33:24.935 --> 00:33:40.654
