Yeah, it was like that—the old oil well. The Oilers. Anybody remember the Oilers?

02:05:13.120 --> 02:05:26.999
They weren't very good; that's why they don't exist. I think they went to Tennessee and they became the Tennessee Titans.

02:05:27.000 --> 02:05:32.882
Houston Oilers. That's who it was. The Houston Oilers. And then they went from there to the Tennessee Titans.

02:05:32.883 --> 02:05:41.150
And then they bought another team and brought them in there, and now they've got a team in Houston that has some kind of something on the side.

02:05:41.151 --> 02:05:48.399
It's like a bull or something. I don't remember. You can tell I don't follow the NFL that well.

02:05:48.400 --> 02:05:52.800
I like my Dallas Cowboys, and that's all I've ever liked since I was a kid.

02:05:52.801 --> 02:06:03.639
The Dallas Cowboys: Troy Aikman, Emmitt Smith, Michael Irvin, Deion Sanders.

02:06:03.640 --> 02:06:13.594
That was a team, boy. I loved to watch that. Well, praise the Lord.

02:06:13.595 --> 02:06:23.235
I guess you know what? I believe that's it. I know we've already been here two hours. I am so thankful for every single one of you. God bless you.

02:06:23.236 --> 02:06:36.946
Thank you for liking, subscribing, clicking the notification bell, doing everything you can to help us pray these things out and stick around and be a part of our beautiful prayer family.

02:06:36.947 --> 02:06:45.279
I'm excited. We're so thankful for every one of you. We love you all so much. Every single one of you. I think it's all interesting.

02:06:45.280 --> 02:06:51.743
There's such a large body of Christ, so many different beliefs and denominations, and we get them all.

02:06:51.744 --> 02:06:55.970
We've got Catholics, we've got Methodists, we've got all kinds of people.

02:06:55.971 --> 02:06:59.174
And the Catholics don't mind the tongues very much, but the Methodists do.

02:06:59.175 --> 02:07:02.785
And then you get the people that are Church of Christ. They just all throw eggs at me.

02:07:02.786 --> 02:07:07.168
But it is interesting because I just keep standing and doing what God's called me to do.

02:07:07.169 --> 02:07:13.427
But it is interesting, the larger this channel grows, that all the different faiths and beliefs come on here.

02:07:13.428 --> 02:07:19.392
We've got the Buddhists who like to watch us. They love us. The Buddhists. Isn't that funny?

02:07:19.393 --> 02:07:26.828
I said the Buddhists like to come over here and watch, and they tell us about Jesus and want to know if they can serve Buddha and Jesus at the same time.

02:07:26.829 --> 02:07:31.945
No, you can't. You either serve one or the other, and you better serve Jesus because the other one's going to take you to hell.

02:07:31.946 --> 02:07:37.383
And that's what I'm trying to tell you all. It's interesting because we had them all. There are a lot of psychics that watch.

02:07:37.384 --> 02:07:44.399
We had a huge psychic witchcraft channel invite us to come on and do a broadcast with them.

02:07:44.400 --> 02:07:51.352
They have hundreds of thousands of subscribers, and they want us to come onto their channel and talk to them about mediums and all kinds of stuff.

02:07:51.353 --> 02:07:56.839
We have all kinds of people watching us and you go, "Wow, that's interesting.

02:07:56.840 --> 02:08:04.830
The devil's crowd wants us to come on their channels."I thought about doing it and telling them about Jesus, but the Lord said no.

02:08:04.831 --> 02:08:21.396
I thought, "Well, I'll go over there and tell them about Jesus because they're all going to hell."But I thought, "Isn't that interesting?"We've got all kinds of psychics and mediums and people talking to devils, and they all say, 'We want to know how you're doing it.'It's Jesus.

02:08:21.398 --> 02:08:32.079
That's how we do it. Jesus helps us. It's not Brandon Biggs. And that's why I think it's interesting because everybody wants to know.

02:08:32.080 --> 02:08:39.620
They had a huge channel, too, didn't they? They come over here and talk, 'We want to interview you.'People are searching.

02:08:39.621 --> 02:08:49.523
I'm like, 'No, I'm not going to go talk on the devil's witchcraft channel because then people think I'm condoning it.'No, I'm just trying to tell them they need to get Jesus.

02:08:49.524 --> 02:09:02.282
They don't know. People are hungry. We get all kinds of people like that—mediums in California, mediums all the time asking, 'Come out to celebrities.

02:09:02.283 --> 02:09:14.439
We want to talk to you.'All glory to Jesus. All hail, King Jesus.

02:09:14.440 --> 02:09:20.759
And I don't take anybody's invitations, really. I get invited to do things, but we really don't, do we?

02:09:20.760 --> 02:09:25.465
We just keep doing our thing unless the Holy Spirit tells us to.

02:09:25.466 --> 02:09:29.173
The only one I really like was Kim Clement's daughter, Donné.

02:09:29.174 --> 02:09:38.639
She is really nice. She was really nice. I love my friend Billy: Billy Burke and Billye Brim, my BBs.

02:09:38.640 --> 02:09:51.875
But we don't do a lot, do we? We kind of just do our thing. Praying in here is a lot—the emails and all the stuff we get by the time we get through our day.

02:09:51.876 --> 02:09:55.993
I'm like, 'How?'because Joseph and they all travel all over the United States of America.

02:09:55.994 --> 02:10:02.945
And I'm like, 'How in the world do they do that?'They have to have huge staffs because, between that, we're exhausted by the time we get our day done.

02:10:02.946 --> 02:10:06.736
And now Joseph goes to all these places, and I say, 'Man,'and he's refreshed.

02:10:06.737 --> 02:10:09.475
A lot of times I talk to him on the phone, and he's not run down.

02:10:09.476 --> 02:10:12.933
He doesn't look like he's whipped. It's very interesting to me.

02:10:12.934 --> 02:10:22.199
I just stay in my vein, stay on my thing. But I'm so thankful that you show up and pray with us.

02:10:22.200 --> 02:10:30.879
It's fine. We love you. We'll be back. What is tomorrow? Friday.

02:10:30.880 --> 02:10:36.859
Yep, I'll be back tomorrow, Friday. We'll pray with you again. I'll try to come on earlier.

02:10:36.860 --> 02:10:40.060
I know it's late and there's a lot of you that are like, 'I have to go do things.

02:10:40.061 --> 02:10:50.159
I don't have time to be up that late and burning the midnight oil.'Yeah, it's the time when we're done feeding Megan and doing all the things we do after we give her dinner.

02:10:50.160 --> 02:10:57.139
I don't mind praying at night, but a lot of people don't. It's after I feed Megan and we do all that we do.

02:10:57.140 --> 02:11:03.919
I'm like, 'Man,'because it's a lot, getting her settled and getting her around so we can pray.

02:11:03.920 --> 02:11:12.999
Got to make sure she's full. But we love you. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:11:13.000 --> 02:11:19.920
Jesus loves you. We love you. We'll see you again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

